      "text": "# 📖 Act 20: Infinite Vault\n**act** · swordsman · narrative · first_person\n\nThe Infinite Vault. Ten artifacts in the Covenant of Humanistic Technologies. An empty eleventh alcove awaits."
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "ada29f5956f8f7e4",
      "text": "> *Covenants do not live in vaults—they live in the copies carried forward by those who passed the threshold.*"
